en Wilkinson, 29\n| 1 dead\n| 2 injured\n| Stephen Wilkinson burst into a mathematics classroom at [[Hall Garth Community Arts College]] and stabbed three children, including 12-year-old Nikki Conroy who later died from her injuries.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/talks-to-comfort-pupils-after-killing-counselling-starts-for-children-still-in-shock-after-classroom-stabbing-malcolm-pithers-reports-1432491.html |title=Talks to comfort pupils after killing: Counselling starts for children still in shock after classroom stabbing |publisher=Independent.co.uk |date=1994-03-30 |accessdate=2011-03-12 |location=London |first=Malcolm |last=Pithers}}</ref>\n|-\n| May 26, 1994\n| [[Union, Kentucky]], United States\n| [[Clay Shrout]], 17\n| 4 dead\n|\n| Clay Shrout kills his mother, father, and two younger sisters before embarking a [[hostage situation]] in a [[trigonometry]] classroom, he's now serving life in prison.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.enquirer.com/editions/2004/05/25/loc_shrout25prison.html |title=Clay Shrout reported of prison behavioral problems |publisher=Enquirer.com |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| June 17, 1994\n| [[Holywood, Northern Ireland]], United Kingdom\n| [[Sullivan Upper School#The 1994 attack|Garnet Bell]], 46\n|\n| 6 injured\n| A former pupil bearing a grudge entered an assembly hall at [[Sullivan Upper School]] and used a [[flamethrower]] to attack students taking [[Advanced Level (UK)|A-Level]] examinations. Six were injured; three seriously, Bell was later sentenced to life behind prison but died there in the hospital wing on March 26, 1997 from cancer.\n|-\n| September 8, 1994\n| [[Hollywood, California]], United States\n|\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Rolando Ruiz, 17, was shot dead on the campus of [[Hollywood High School]]. Police suspected that the shooting was [[gang]]-related.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://articles.latimes.com/1994-09-08/local/me-35928_1_hollywood-high-school |title=10th-Grader Slain at Hollywood High as Ri