ga, Alabama]], United States\n| Steven L. Curry, 16\n| 1 dead\n|\n| 16-year-old student Steven L. Curry fatally shot 18-year-old student Bobby Roberson Jr. in the parking lot of Talladega High School.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CL&s_site=ledgerenquirer&p_multi=CL&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB59509AFB53C8F&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |title=Students mourn death of peer shot outside school |publisher=Nl.newsbank.com |date=1996-04-14 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| September 25, 1996\n| [[Scottdale, Georgia]], United States\n| David Dubose Jr., 16\n| 1 dead\n|\n| David Dubose Jr. shot and killed 49-year-old English teacher Horace P. Morgan with a .38 caliber revolver in a corridor of DeKalb Alternative School. Dubose was then subdued by staff members.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=348&dat=19960926&id=SrQFAAAAIBAJ&sjid=cjMDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3037,7959360 |title=Teen faces murder charges for shooting school teacher |publisher=News.google.com |date=1996-09-26 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| January 27, 1997\n| [[West Palm Beach, Florida]], United States\n| Tronneal Mangum, 13\n| 1 dead\n|\n| 13-year-old Tronneal Mangum shot and killed another student, 14-year-old John Kamel, in front of Conniston Middle School. Mangum was reportedly upset that Kamel had failed to repay a $40 debt.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/tampatribune/access/38357159.html?dids=38357159:38357159&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jan+28%2C+1997&author=&pub=Tampa+Tribune&desc=Pupil+killed+in+dispute+over+%2440%3B+classmate+charged&pqatl=google |title=Pupil killed in dispute over $40; classmate charged |publisher=Pqasb.pqarchiver.com |date=1997-01-28 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| February 19, 1997\n| [[Bethel, Alaska]], United States\n| [[Evan Ramsey]], 16\n| 2 dead\n| 2 injured\n| Armed with a