on for shooting|date=April 15, 2010| url =\nhttp://wcfcourier.com/news/local/update-mark-becker-sentenced-to-life-in-prison-for-shooting/article_6b82c7aa-47ea-11df-a5f8-001cc4c002e0.html|work= [[WCF Courier]]|accessdate = September 1, 2013|author=Nelson, Josh}}</ref>\n|-\n| July 16, 2009\n| [[Manzini, Manzini District, Swaziland|Ncabaneni]], [[Swaziland]]\n| Sicelo Dlamini, 22\n| 2 dead\n| 10 injured\n| Three boys and eight girls were stabbed with a [[spear]] by Sicelo Dlamini at classrooms in Ncabaneni High School, in [[Manzini, Manzini District, Swaziland|Ncabaneni]], [[Swaziland]], who was then chased and beaten to death by a mob of outraged students. Besides Dlamini, one of the wounded girls died at the scene.<ref>[http://www.observer.org.sz/index.php?news=5814 Murder at Ncabaneni High] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716055111/http://www.observer.org.sz/index.php?news=5814 |date=2011-07-16 }}, ''The Swazi Observer'' (July 17, 2009)</ref><ref>[http://www.observer.org.sz/index.php?news=5915 \u2018Lunatic\u2019 had not taken medication] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716055125/http://www.observer.org.sz/index.php?news=5915 |date=2011-07-16 }}, ''The Swazi Observer'' (July 21, 2009)</ref>\n|-\n| August 24, 2009\n| [[San Mateo, California|San Mateo]],<br>[[California]],<br>United States\n| Alex Robert Youshock, 17\n|\n|\n| Two [[pipe bomb]]s went off in a hallway of [[Hillsdale High School (San Mateo, California)|Hillsdale High School]], in [[San Mateo, California]], during the beginning of first period classes.<ref name=\"sfgate824\">{{cite news|first=Jaxon| last=Van Derbeken| title=\n'Techno-wizard' teen suspect fooled family|date=2009-08-25|work=San Francisco Chronicle|url =\nhttp://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2009/08/25/BAL719DH0L.DTL|accessdate = 2009-08-25}}</ref> Nobody was injured from the explosions.<ref name=\"ktvu824\">{{cite news|title=School Attacker Had 10 Pipe Bombs, Sword, Chainsaw|date=2009-08-24|pu